description: Battery Point is one of the oldest parts of Hobart and the City Council is about to put into practice a development plan which will retain the character and charm of this area. Shows the signal station, the seamen's cottages, the fine houses of the wealthy, Kelly's Steps, St George's Church and other historic items.
